name: Natureal Beauty (V-Neck) - Black or Plum
description:
"Be real"......Let your natureal beauty show! These fashionable tees are for natural women who have natural beauty within but would like to stand out. With "be real" in metallic gold....your ever-changing hair will always be bold. 

***Available in S - XXL*** 

Available Colors: Black and Plum 

This fashionable tee is screen printed on a Bella fitted tee made of 100% fine ring-spun combed cotton. This lightweight fine jersey is ultra soft and form fitting. 

Suggested Care: 
For best results hand wash shirt in cold water inside out to maintain print. Hang dry your tees, rather than tumble dry them – the less friction the better! Turn tee inside out to iron.

**PLEASE EMAIL thinkkinkz@gmail.com to make sure we have your size available. We sell out of certain sizes faster than others and we can add your size to our next printing.
